Author: GitHub
Title: Meet Ducky, your new open source coding buddy
Description:
Meet Ducky, your new open source coding buddy! We've put the 3D print files for our fan-favorite mascot on GitHub so you can print your own. He's cute, he's a great listener, and he's here to help you with all your rubber duck debugging needs.

Drop by the Makerspace at #GitHubUniverse to learn more or download Rubber Ducky from http://gh.io/octoprints to create your own.

Get your passes for GitHub Universe: https://githubuniverse.com/?utm\_source=YouTube&utm\_medium=Social&utm\_campaign=community

#Ducky #GitHub #OpenSource
